the buyers.

DOC.LD:
Eureka--The Taste of Main Street on April 4 will precede the Redwood
Coast Dixieland Jazz Festival, featuring food, music and dancing
April 5-7. Old Town Eureka. 5-8 p.m. April 4; noon-2 a.m. April 5;

DOC.TE:
   The government promises to protect Nanchizi's heritage. But scale
models suggest only four old houses and the temple will be spared;
everything else will face the "demolish" order.

