DOC.TE:
   It is dangerous to compare past with present. More women play now;
more big, strong women play now. Coaching is better, from grade
school to college. Facilities are better, opportunities are greater.

DOC.LD:
   Deputy Chief Maurice Moore, 66, retired in January as investigators
from the LAPD and FBI probed his financial ties to his son, Kevin Moore,
a convicted cocaine trafficker.

